metadata.name: The sky was all purple, there were people runnin' everywhere
metadata.description:
"War is all around us  
My mind says prepare to fight"

This picture is about the chaotic feeling that the end of the world is near. However, I also feel that something better is coming in the near future. Maybe I choose to look back two decades and party like it's year 1999.

The work of art is the digitization of the painting that bears the same name. An acrylic painting with some holographic touches and some yellow vinyl textures, also a kind of little crystals.  
The physical piece has measurements: 24x17cm.
